data.description: **MOTIVATED SELLER** $6,000 TOWARDS CLOSING! Welcome to this meticulously maintained home nestled in the sought-after Alamo Ranch community. Listed BELOW MARKET VALUE! Boasting over 2,100 square feet of comfortable living space, this residence offers both style and functionality. Elegant granite countertops in the kitchen and water softener adds a touch of luxury to everyday living. WATER SOFTENER, WASHER/DRYER/, STAINLESS STEEL REFRIGERATOR ALL INCLUDED!! 3 spacious bedroom, 2 full baths, and a bonus office room all well-maintained, while showcasing pride of ownership. Don't miss the opportunity to make this gorgeous one-story residence your own.
